title: Christina Perri &ndash; Head Or Heart (2014) 320kbps
description:
Head or Heart is the second studio album from American singer Christina Perri. Working with a quartet of producers (Martin Johnson, Jake Gosling, John Hill, and Butch Walker), as well as with British singer Ed Sheeran on the track "Be My Forever," Perri produces her most confident record to date. It also includes the single "Human."
